The paper deals with image recognition tasks and the joint representation of vision and language information, which are typically studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks and residual learning also suggests the paper may belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper specifically focuses on multimodality, which is a topic studied in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
